item.title: Internship at the Toronto Dominion Bank Jan 2024 - April 2024
item.description: Reflection on my Internship at TD Bank Between Jan 2024 and April 2024 I interned at TD Bank, one of the leading banks in Canada. Here are my thoughts on my experience and what I learned. To sum everything up, there are three key areas which I noticed are different than my previous internship at the Government of Ontario: Trust business, lots of people, Change Management.
